item.description:
Join us for our first 5K of 2010 to support Hollis School in Braintree.

Joggers, Walkers and Joggers in training!
If you are part of our training group, this will be the start of week 7 and a nice way to see where you are at. It isn't a bad thing if you walk part of it! :)

Hollis School 14th Annual 5K Road Race
Sunday, June 6th
Race starts at 10:30 am, but we can meet as a group around 10am.
Braintree HS
**Near the Tennis Courts!**

Entry fee:
$18 by June 1st
$20 on the day of the race
Tee Shirts to the first 200 Registered Runners
There will also be raffle tickets being sold at the event and refreshments following the race.

Race is sanctioned by USATF

RAIN or SHINE

Registration can be found in "files" under the "more" tab for our group (after 5/12). Please mail your registration and entry fee directly to them or bring it with you the day of the event.

SSFMG and its organizers are not responsible for any injuries to participants.
